data.name: fileContentExcludeExplicitCaptureCheckBox.ToolTip
data.value: Specifies that the only valid captures are explicitly named or numbered groups of the form (?<name>…). This allows unnamed parentheses to act as noncapturing groups without the syntactic clumsiness of the expression (?:…).
